summary: This is an email from an FBI agent regarding the completion of a photo sourcing project for trial preparation, which includes an attached spreadsheet with evidence item IDs, CD names, and item locations. The document is subject to a protective order covering specific paragraphs.

events.title: Photo Project Completion Email
events.description: An FBI agent sends an email stating that the photo sourcing project is completed and attached, with added columns for evidence item ID, name of CD, and location of item.

keyFacts: A photo sourcing project for trial preparation was completed by the FBI as of November 26, 2021.
The project output includes a spreadsheet with evidence item IDs, CD names, and item locations.
The document is subject to a protective order covering paragraphs 7, 8, 9, 10, 15, and 17.
